translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すぐに行くとサテラが出る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you go immediately, Satera will appear.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アメージング城内
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Inside Amazing Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サテラがかけつけると
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When Satera rushes over,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 学者が率いてる部隊が子供達に負けた所
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's the place where the troop led by the scholar was defeated by the children.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きさまら・・・とサテラが怒って現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You... Satera appears angrily.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセット．サテラさん、すみませんが魔王ランスと戦う時に邪魔されては困るので
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset: Satera-san, sorry, but we can't have you interfering when fighting Demon King Rance,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 動けなくさせてもらいますとか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so I'll have to immobilize you or something.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 生意気な事を言うな、ん・・ダークランス、お前もいたのか・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't say such cheeky things. Hmm... Dark Rance, you were here too...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サテラが立ち向かうとするが、足が竦む・・本能的にかなわないと分かった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Satera tries to confront him, but her legs freeze... instinctively realizing she can't win.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シーザーがそれを見て、サテラ様と不安そうに言うが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Caesar sees this and anxiously says, 'Lady Satera...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: えーい、となんとか勇気を振り絞って突撃するサテラ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With a yell, Satera somehow musters her courage and charges.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Battle

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 城内に侵入する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Infiltrate inside the castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ビスケッタさんが一人でいます
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Biscetta-san is alone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスのご子息の方々、旦那様になんのご用でしょうか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sons of Rance, may I ask what your business is with the master?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Choice

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞魔王を倒しに来た
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Came to defeat the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: というと、私の立場ではそういう返事を頂くと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you say that, from my position, receiving such an answer,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦わざるえませんと戦闘になります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have no choice but to fight, so it leads to battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし、エール達の敵ではなく軽く倒れます
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, she is no match for Ale and the others and is easily defeated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞ランスに会いに来た
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Came to see Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遠い所をようこそ、疲れておいでのようなので旦那様に会われる前に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Welcome from afar. You seem tired, so before seeing the master,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少し休憩をして身支度を調えたらをお奨めします
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I recommend you rest a little and prepare yourself.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 休憩になります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It will transition to rest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王城の最上階にまで上り詰めて魔王ランスと対峙する。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Climb to the top floor of the Demon King's castle and confront Demon King Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すでにかなり邪悪になっている魔王ランス。人間だった頃の記憶はありません。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Rance has become quite evil by now. He has no memory of his human days.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール達が来ても気にした様子はなく彫像を見ながら茶など飲んでいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He pays no attention when Ale and the others arrive, drinking tea while looking at a statue.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットは、それが氷柱シィルである事に気がつく、どうしてあれが・・と
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset notices that it is the icicle Shīru, wondering why it is that...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 思うが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He thinks, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールか誰かが魔王ランスに話しかけ、そのまま戦闘となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ale or someone speaks to Demon King Rance, and it immediately leads to battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王を倒そうと思わなくていい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You don't have to try to defeat the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 負けないように慎重な戦い、チャンスを待つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fight carefully to avoid losing, and wait for an opportunity.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王に隙が出来た時、リセットさん、お願いします
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When the Demon King shows an opening, Reset-san, please.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ええ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットがランスにビンタ、成功
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset slaps Rance, successfully.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ランスが怒り、リセットの手を握りしめる、リセット潰されそうになるが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Rance gets angry, grabs Reset's hand tightly, and nearly crushes Reset, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは正気に戻った。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance returns to his senses.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・・ん、あっ・・くそっ、またお前にビンタされたのか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Hm, ah... damn, you slapped me again?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ごめんね、お父さん
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm sorry, Daddy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 設定．人間ランス的な所まで性格が戻った訳では無いです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Note: His personality hasn't fully returned to human Rance levels.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自分は魔王である事を自覚しており、抑えないといけない存在である
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He is aware that he is the Demon King and must suppress his nature.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なのに、また魔王に心を支配されつつあったのか、くそっ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yet, he was again being controlled by the Demon King in his heart, damn it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール、ザンス・・他、子供達・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ale, Zansu... and the other children...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスが落ち着いたのを見て・・せ成功したのか・・ほっとしている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seeing that Rance has calmed down... did we succeed? They feel relieved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ん、俺のガキどもか、なかなかがんばったな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, my kids, huh? You did pretty well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お父さん、それより、これ・・と彫像を指差すリセット
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Dad, more importantly, this... Reset points at the statue.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ああ、それか、サテラが持って来た彫像だが、なんか気になって・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, that? It's the statue that Satera brought, but it kind of bothers me...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: えっ・・えっ・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eh... eh...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィル！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shīru!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットがビンタを入れるチャンスもないまま戦いは長引いた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The fight dragged on without Reset even having a chance to slap him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール達は強かった、人類始まって以来のまさに最強の戦闘集団
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ale and the others were strong, truly the strongest combat group since the dawn of humanity.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、そのエール達ですら魔王ランスにはかなわなかった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, even Ale and the others could not defeat Demon King Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 徐々においつめられる、一人また一人と倒れていく・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They were gradually cornered, one after another falling...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここ、何名か倒れる様子入れれたらかっこいいかな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here, maybe it would look cool if some got knocked down.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットも吹き飛ばされた、それを庇った誰かも倒れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset was also blown away, and someone who tried to protect him also fell.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ダークランスが鬼畜アタックを使い、そして突っ込んできたカオスを突き刺す。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Dark Rance uses the brutal attack and stabs the charging Chaos.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ランスはダークランスを蹴り飛ばし、突き刺さったカオスを持つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Rance kicks Dark Rance away and grabs the pierced Chaos.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カオス「えーい、離せ、離せ、魔王に心を委ねたお前など鷲の主ではないわ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Chaos: "Hey! Let go, let go! Someone who has surrendered their heart to the Demon King is no master of the Eagle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 認めない者が持つと悪の波動で心が壊れてしまうぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If someone who doesn't accept this holds it, their mind will be broken by the evil waves."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すぐに行くとサテラが出る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you go immediately, Satera will appear.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アメージング城内
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Inside Amazing Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サテラがかけつけると
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When Satera rushes over,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 学者が率いてる部隊が子供達に負けた所
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's the place where the troop led by the scholar was defeated by the children.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きさまら・・・とサテラが怒って現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You... Satera appears angrily.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセット．サテラさん、すみませんが魔王ランスと戦う時に邪魔されては困るので
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset: Satera-san, sorry, but we can't have you interfering when fighting Demon King Rance,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 動けなくさせてもらいますとか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so I'll have to immobilize you or something.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 生意気な事を言うな、ん・・ダークランス、お前もいたのか・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't say such cheeky things. Hmm... Dark Rance, you were here too...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サテラが立ち向かうとするが、足が竦む・・本能的にかなわないと分かった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Satera tries to confront him, but her legs freeze... instinctively realizing she can't win.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シーザーがそれを見て、サテラ様と不安そうに言うが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Caesar sees this and anxiously says, 'Lady Satera...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: えーい、となんとか勇気を振り絞って突撃するサテラ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With a yell, Satera somehow musters her courage and charges.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Battle

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 城内に侵入する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Infiltrate inside the castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ビスケッタさんが一人でいます
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Biscetta-san is alone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスのご子息の方々、旦那様になんのご用でしょうか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sons of Rance, may I ask what your business is with the master?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Choice

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞魔王を倒しに来た
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Came to defeat the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: というと、私の立場ではそういう返事を頂くと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you say that, from my position, receiving such an answer,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦わざるえませんと戦闘になります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I have no choice but to fight, so it leads to battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし、エール達の敵ではなく軽く倒れます
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, she is no match for Ale and the others and is easily defeated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞ランスに会いに来た
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Came to see Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遠い所をようこそ、疲れておいでのようなので旦那様に会われる前に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Welcome from afar. You seem tired, so before seeing the master,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 少し休憩をして身支度を調えたらをお奨めします
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I recommend you rest a little and prepare yourself.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 休憩になります
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It will transition to rest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王城の最上階にまで上り詰めて魔王ランスと対峙する。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Climb to the top floor of the Demon King's castle and confront Demon King Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すでにかなり邪悪になっている魔王ランス。人間だった頃の記憶はありません。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Rance has become quite evil by now. He has no memory of his human days.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール達が来ても気にした様子はなく彫像を見ながら茶など飲んでいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He pays no attention when Ale and the others arrive, drinking tea while looking at a statue.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットは、それが氷柱シィルである事に気がつく、どうしてあれが・・と
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset notices that it is the icicle Shīru, wondering why it is that...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 思うが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He thinks, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールか誰かが魔王ランスに話しかけ、そのまま戦闘となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ale or someone speaks to Demon King Rance, and it immediately leads to battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王を倒そうと思わなくていい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You don't have to try to defeat the Demon King.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 負けないように慎重な戦い、チャンスを待つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fight carefully to avoid losing, and wait for an opportunity.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王に隙が出来た時、リセットさん、お願いします
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When the Demon King shows an opening, Reset-san, please.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ええ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットがランスにビンタ、成功
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset slaps Rance, successfully.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ランスが怒り、リセットの手を握りしめる、リセット潰されそうになるが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Rance gets angry, grabs Reset's hand tightly, and nearly crushes Reset, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは正気に戻った。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance returns to his senses.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ・・・・ん、あっ・・くそっ、またお前にビンタされたのか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Hm, ah... damn, you slapped me again?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ごめんね、お父さん
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm sorry, Daddy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 設定．人間ランス的な所まで性格が戻った訳では無いです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Note: His personality hasn't fully returned to human Rance levels.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自分は魔王である事を自覚しており、抑えないといけない存在である
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He is aware that he is the Demon King and must suppress his nature.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なのに、また魔王に心を支配されつつあったのか、くそっ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yet, he was again being controlled by the Demon King in his heart, damn it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール、ザンス・・他、子供達・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ale, Zansu... and the other children...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスが落ち着いたのを見て・・せ成功したのか・・ほっとしている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seeing that Rance has calmed down... did we succeed? They feel relieved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ん、俺のガキどもか、なかなかがんばったな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, my kids, huh? You did pretty well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お父さん、それより、これ・・と彫像を指差すリセット
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Dad, more importantly, this... Reset points at the statue.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ああ、それか、サテラが持って来た彫像だが、なんか気になって・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, that? It's the statue that Satera brought, but it kind of bothers me...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: えっ・・えっ・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eh... eh...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィル！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shīru!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットがビンタを入れるチャンスもないまま戦いは長引いた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The fight dragged on without Reset even having a chance to slap him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール達は強かった、人類始まって以来のまさに最強の戦闘集団
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ale and the others were strong, truly the strongest combat group since the dawn of humanity.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、そのエール達ですら魔王ランスにはかなわなかった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, even Ale and the others could not defeat Demon King Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 徐々においつめられる、一人また一人と倒れていく・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They were gradually cornered, one after another falling...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここ、何名か倒れる様子入れれたらかっこいいかな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here, maybe it would look cool if some got knocked down.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットも吹き飛ばされた、それを庇った誰かも倒れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset was also blown away, and someone who tried to protect him also fell.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ダークランスが鬼畜アタックを使い、そして突っ込んできたカオスを突き刺す。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Dark Rance uses the brutal attack and stabs the charging Chaos.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ランスはダークランスを蹴り飛ばし、突き刺さったカオスを持つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon King Rance kicks Dark Rance away and grabs the pierced Chaos.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カオス「えーい、離せ、離せ、魔王に心を委ねたお前など鷲の主ではないわ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Chaos: "Hey! Let go, let go! Someone who has surrendered their heart to the Demon King is no master of the Eagle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 認めない者が持つと悪の波動で心が壊れてしまうぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If someone who doesn't accept this holds it, their mind will be broken by the evil waves."
